You can create an idea for a specific opportunity. You must provide a specific title for the idea and type a brief description of the idea that you want to create

If the FTE benefit is applicable for an idea, you must specify information such as, the FTE benefits associated with the idea, the customer benefits associated with the idea, and the organization benefits associated with the idea regardless of the workflow associated with the idea. You must further specify the benefit related information, such as the estimated hard dollar benefit for the idea, the estimated soft dollar benefit for the idea, the estimated cost of investment for the idea, the qualitative benefits associated with the idea, the number of efforts saved, in hours, the estimated date on which the FTE is released, the estimated date on which the benefit realization cycle (BRC) starts and the hard dollar value for annualized revenue associated with the idea.
